item.title: Need help with hybridscape!~!~
item.dc:creator: @Hell_Hound Hell Hound
item.description:
@Hell_Hound wrote:

Ok you must own a server and be running it to play on moparscape period, unless your playing on someone elses you have to enter there IP, but to enter moparscape on the IP of 127.0.0.1 you must be running the server on your computer.

Go to this download and download this Private Server Source. http://www.p16.dodian.com/Project16_V.4.5.rar

After you have the file, open it, click right on the icon Compiler, click edit.

Highlight all of that and replace it with this:

@echo off
title Server
color A
“C:\Program Files\java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_09\bin\java.exe” server
pause

Save and close, then double click on it, after is says starting server etc. etc. try logging in.

GOOD LUCK ;D
